Package: easyVerification
Title: Forecast verification metrics for large datasets
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2014-12-17
Authors@R: c(person("Jonas", "Bhend", email = "jonas.bhend@meteoswiss.ch",
    role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jacopo", "Ripoldi", role="ctb"),
    person("Claudia", "Mignani", role="ctb"),
    person("Irina", "Mahlstein", role="ctb"),
    person("Rebecca", "Hiller", role="ctb"),
    person("Christoph", "Spirig", role="ctb"),
    person("Mark", "Liniger", role="ctb"))
Description: This package provides functions to simplify application of
    forecast verification metrcis to large datasets. The forecast metrics are
    imported from the SpecsVerification package, and additional forecast metrics
    are provided with this package. Alternatively, new forecast
    scores can be implemented using the example scores provided in this
    package.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0),
    SpecsVerification
Suggests:
    testthat
